@Robot
#end
:touch
#zap touch
Robot: Can you please find some way to
get me out of here? My controls were
packed away in those storage bins to the
West.

I would be forever grateful.
#end
:touch
Robot: Oh thank heavens! I am free! You
have no idea how much this means to me.
Thank you so very much.
/i
Robot: If you would be so kind as to
direct me out of this complex, purchase
a water vessal, sail the seas as free as
can be, settle down on the mainland,
start a beautiful robot family, and
initiate a successful business in
automating people out of work, I would
appreciate it a lot.
/i/i/i/i/i/i/i
:touch
Robot: ...Why are you frowning?

