@HowTo
#end
:a
#lock
Unpack and arrange the old controls from
the containers. When you are happy with
the position of a control, shoot it with
a bullet to activate it. Shoot it again
to deactivate and move it around some
more.

(Warning: Some effort has been made in
preventing the objects or player from
becoming boxed in, however it could still
potentially happen.

